<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">A short, 8 page story called &quot;Axolotl&quot; by Julio Cortázar – it has many connections w/ Borges&apos;s Labyrinths collection and &quot;The Aleph&quot;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">A short, 8 page story called "Axolotl" by Julio Cortázar – it has many connections w/ Borges's Labyrinths collection and "The Aleph"<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
